data.description: Experience the Luxury in this 5 year old, 3/2 +Den Spacious 1900 SqFt home offering Expansive Views of the Intersecting Freshwater Canal! Raised Trey Ceilings with Crown Molding elevates the ambiance as you step into the Open Floor Plan. The kitchen boasts Raised Soft-Close Cabinets, Sleek Quartz Countertops, stunning Tile Backsplash, and Stainless-Steel Appliances. LVP Flooring provides a seamless, carpet-free environment. The Primary Suite features Trey Ceilings, Crown Molding, Large Walk-In Closets, and a Resort-style Bathroom highlighting Dual Sinks with Quartz Countertops, a Walk-Through Shower with Beautiful Tile Listello, two Benches and an additional Linen Closet. The Laundry Room is equipped with a Utility Sink, Folding Station, and Granite. The Guest Bath serves as a pool bath showcasing Granite and opens to the Expansive Backyard surrounded by a 6 Ft. Privacy Fence—ready for your Pool. In addition there are HURRICANE IMPACT WINDOWS throughout! Embrace the outdoors on the Oversized, Wood Paneled Under Truss Lanai and experience over 4 miles of waterways. This home is located south of Pine Island Corridor offering convenient access to shopping, dining, and grocery options!
